reviews.review_text:
thanks this show is incredible!

Joan Baez backed by the Dead, singing Bobby Mcgee about her days with Bobby Dylan!!!

Jerry was stoked and his playing is fantatic. Big Boss Man is great! ..he nails the jam at the end or GDTRFB like it was a good night in 1971!

and then joan singing Its all over now baby blue with jerry!!!!!!!!!!!

not the clearest but a classic

Well, well, well... This show is quite the shit. The Shakedown opener has just become one of my favorite performances. Jerry is playing his brains out! Solid show, okay sound quality. Thanks for cleaning this up Charlie!
